Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:19.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Senpai (Gloomlord)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evening! What's up, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry this is out of the blue, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please: be with me. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:52.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:13.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 7: I Want to Hang Out\Nat a Cat Café and a Pub!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please: be with me. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I know this is sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you asked me to be with you?\NOn the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't seem\Nto bring myself to go in alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to the cat café!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God you're here! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:03:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, I can't wait!\NThis is my first time--I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What--hey! Quit kicking--ow!\NStop! Cut it out! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party of two?\NTake off your shoes and go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have cats, Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. They have cats, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, duh. We {\i1}are {\i0}a cat café.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can touch them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Senpai. You've got those scary eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cats are okay with it,\Ngo right ahead and pet them gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like I taught you earlier: from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance! Cats like being scratched\Nunder their chins or behind their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki, look! A cat--on my lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't be too loud, or it'll run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't get this excited around humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that gloominess must be\Nkeeping some stuff repressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cootchie, cootchie, coo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so creepy that I don't even mind\Nthe {\i1}extremely {\i0}misleading way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he got me here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too overjoyed for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Uzaki, what's with that plastered-on smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking how creepy it is that\Nyou act so cool, but you like cute things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what? Jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. My true feelings slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:05:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}also {\i0}creepy that you're careful\Nto speak quietly so as not to spook the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your true feelings are showing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I {\i1}am {\i0}glad you came today.\NI'd get to the entrance and do a U-turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my birthday's actually coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning 20, so I'd like to make it sorta special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs are so numb that\NI haven't processed anything you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get rid of the cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't have a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll just move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was finally on my lap!\NJust a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncross your legs already\Nand get those pins and needles out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a quick-fix kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out! What the hell? Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just {\i1}so {\i0}wide open,\Nyou were practically {\i1}asking {\i0}for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! {\i1}Everybody's {\i0}wide open\Nwhen their legs are numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so loud, now--you'll scare the kitty-cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokety poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokety, pokety poke-poke-poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokety, pokety, pokety, pokety poke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez, what now? This is really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might just awaken something in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki... please... uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color is your blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save that kind of play for home, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Play"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Play"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, what a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that fun, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first half was. Then {\i1}you {\i0}got us thrown out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Next time I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably can't go back there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta love cat cafés, though.\NLots of friendly kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? They were so used to being around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Very Easy Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your communication level is puny.\NLevel 5? Too bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they still warmed up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a gun-toting old man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have cats at home, but it's good\Nto interact with different cats sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what married men\Nwho go to cabaret clubs feel like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me! What a horrible analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I owe you one for today,\Nso think it over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've already thought {\i1}that {\i0}over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I mentioned earlier,\Nmy birthday is coming up. August 7th!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have high hopes, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Asia Café"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she said she has high hopes for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}do {\i0}seem like you'd\Nbe bad at that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anticipating that Sakurai would be bad at this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then throwing him for a loop\Nwith vague "high hopes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite the schemer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that comes from the\Npeculiar mentality of a girl in love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who wants someone to fret over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that Hana realizes it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, any way you look at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're going to eat this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers, because my name means "flower"?\NSo you suck at puns, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally the wrong size!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, only hotties can get away\Nwith giving a present like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have given me\Na uTunes card instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want those special-event bonuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like anything\NI give her will be a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure doesn't have an eye for flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A placeholder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it has multiplayer!\NI'll play with you, loner senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be happy with anything Sakurai gives her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about this\Ntoo much--I'm just so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you follow your intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her the first thing that came\Nto mind when you heard "birthday present."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing that came to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"August 7th"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I still have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to pick something today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki (Idiot)"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Uzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be with me! I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Uzaki, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:06.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pub"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to spring this on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, on the phone...\Nyou said you wanted me to be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't bring myself to go in alone!\NCome with me, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your treat! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember? My 20th birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have high hopes, you know--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for your wallet, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"High hopes" --you mean you were\Nangling for a pub visit all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong? C'mon, let's go in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrating your milestone 20th at a pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, totally! I wanted to try drinking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking's fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on the drinker,\Non the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No guarantees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's {\i1}not {\i0}fun,\Nyou can do something to {\i1}make {\i0}it fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just enjoy ourselves, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a soft drink, but also... not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it taste good or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this, like,\Nburning in my throat. Deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's beer like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is beer! It's bitter,\Nbut there's more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it goes so great\Nwith fried and salty food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take a slug of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Isn't that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They go {\i1}fantastic {\i0}together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beer resets the grease from the chicken\Nfor fresh new flavor with every bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you really chugged it.\NSo what's your verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}great{\i0}! So you drink alcohol with food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people savor it on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter as long\Nas you're enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:14:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, as you so kindly suggested,\NI'm gonna do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right--go on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just how much are you ordering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wallet is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Cancel! Cancel those!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidebu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No horsing around, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Quit screwing around or--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yow{\i0}! Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is {\i0}this?{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:34.70,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Russian Roulette Octopus Balls"\N"Only 1 is Super Spicy!"\N"8 for ¥550"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like one of them is ultra spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beer! Beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no water, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki, a drink! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a sec, okay? I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}can't {\i0}wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I bet {\i1}I {\i0}can make {\i1}this {\i0}one.\NI should make it for you sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you: make it snappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is good!\NI think I might like {\i1}yuzu {\i0}liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait just one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really knocking 'em back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy--it {\i1}is {\i0}your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your {\i1}yuzu {\i0}liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}too fast{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine? How many is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.\NDrink some water in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just might be a heavyweight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just slow down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait! Your {\i1}yuzu {\i0}liqueur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay there, Senpai? You're kinda wobbly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one wobbling around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She started out okay but\Nturned out pretty much as I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jotted down how much you drank.\NStay under that amount next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Senpai, you sure got tall all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a utility pole! Walk properly, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, c'mon, Senpai, carry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piggyback! Baby back... ribs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Your various...\Nareas... are all up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Various areas? Whazzat mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's touchin' where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, she is one irritating drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooshy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Markin' you with my scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way can I send her home on her own like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, stand up. I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw! I'm not goin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink at {\i1}your {\i0}place, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, more drinking?! Go home and get to sleep, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stand up already! I can see your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you callin' a dummy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Senpai, d'you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! That late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, too bad! No more trains! Ha ha! You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're {\i0}the dummy who can't get home, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can call a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzaki's dumbass drinking drained me dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ATM should still be running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, but that access fee... and taxis\Nwill be charging pricey late-night fares...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her stay over? I could never!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think straight with this booze in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't abandon your junior,\Nstuck away from home, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this was\Nall calculated from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the convenience store.\NI want some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And alcohol!\NI wanna verify my age! 'Cause I'm 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just so you know,\NI only have one futon set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm splitting it up, moron! One quilt each!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai... Hey, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to sleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, let me sleep.\NIt's three in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You play dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}still {\i0}drinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... She needs to learn\Nabout the horrors of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squid's yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No--come morning, she'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh... I really am sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll just sleep right here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No stun-locking moves this time,\Nso let's get sparrin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? Hey, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? Are you asleep for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving behind your junior\Nand just... going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he'll wake up if I kiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I {\i1}knew {\i0}you were only faking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a joke--a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure were frantic there, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you never been kissed, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Shut up! Go to sleep, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleepytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts... I feel awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's called a hangover.\NLife's going to suck for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are {\i1}you {\i0}just fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-ups drink in moderation\Nso {\i1}that {\i0}doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "modera" --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Everyone has an alcohol screw-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing your first time wasn't\Nat some sketchy drinking party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you found your limit right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in lecture mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't drink much water, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes water to metabolize alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternate with drinks of water\Nand you won't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel better by noon.\NJust have to tough it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the screw-up, the better the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, drink as much water as you do booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'S fine. I won't drink again as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably for the best.\NThough everyone with a hangover says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never... ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hit the store--\Nyou hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot... for being with me... at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I nearly forgot: You're 20 now, Uzaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:44.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 8: I Want to Watch Fireworks Together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sak!